reviewText:
Early Access Review

Con: rarely over 1,000 players online at any given moment (THEREFORE, NO RANKED PVP MATCHING); but you can still start a pvp game at any given moment;
replay controls are too simple (can only pause or play forward through time); PAY-TO-WIN-QUICKLY;

Highly customizeable loadouts!_ once you aquire enough in-game $$$ and buy enough pilots, parts, and units.

It's a free game.  small download.  been around since 2011, starting as a NativeClient Chrome app, then moved to PC and steam.
